Quam vulgaris fuerit fructus, vel inde elucet, quod
<lb/>ponderis species e seminibus desumeretur. <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ὀβολός</foreign> enim
<lb/>aequiparabaturs sesquilupino (<foreign xml:lang="grc">ἔχει θέρμον αςʹ</foreign>): lupinus <foreign xml:lang="grc">κε-</foreign><lb break="no"/><foreign xml:lang="grc">ράτια βʹ</foreign>: <foreign xml:lang="grc">κεράτιον χαλκοῦς βʹ</foreign> continebat. Scrupulus vero
<lb/>(<foreign xml:lang="grc">τὸ γράμμα</foreign>) sex habebat <foreign xml:lang="grc">κεράτια</foreign><ref target="#fn36">36</ref>, unde patet, <foreign xml:lang="grc">κεράτιον</foreign>
